Name: Dark Sweeper
About the game: Dark Sweeper - a shooter about a soldier, which takes place in the wastelands filled with various creatures and marauders. You are a young corporal sent to a military operation, your task is to defeat the enemies. You will find yourself in a dangerous area, completely alone. Find the right weapon and go to destroy your enemies. But remember you must stay alive. Game Features: - Pixel graphics - Nice soundtrack - Lots of levels
